---
// CTA final
---
<section class="section section-dark" id="contact" aria-labelledby="cta-title">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cta-final-inner">
      <h2 class="cta-final-h2" id="cta-title">Parlons de<br />votre projet.</h2>
      <p class="cta-final-sub">
        30 minutes. Sans engagement. Je vous dis honnêtement si je peux vous aider et comment.
      </p>
      <a
        href="https://cal.com/steve-deguilly/30min"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener"
        class="cta-final-btn"
      >Réserver un premier échange →</a>
      <p class="cta-meta">Via Cal.com · Visio ou téléphone · Réponse sous 24h</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cta-final-inner {
    text-align: center;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 24px;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .cta-final-h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 40px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: -0.015em;
    color: var(--color-bg-cream);
    line-height: 1.15;
    margin: 0;
  }
  @media (max-width: 767px) { .cta-final-h2 { font-size: 28px; } }
  .cta-final-sub {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 17px;
    color: var(--color-text-on-dark);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .cta-final-btn {
    background: var(--color-accent-cta);
    color: #FFFFFF;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 15px 28px;
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 500;
    cursor: pointer;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background 150ms;
  }
  .cta-final-btn:hover { background: var(--color-accent-cta-hover); }
  .cta-meta {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--color-text-on-dark-muted);
    margin: 0;
  }
</style>
